/uploads/2024/10/08014409/TobyThyerPhotography-1-2.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/workshop-keeping-subaru-wrc-cars-japanese-public-roads/tobythyerphotography-1-2-8/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08014409/TobyThyerPhotography-1-2-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe 2024 D1GP R2-winning Toyota GR86, powered by a Nissan R35 GT-R VR38DETT, is parked alongside. The new engine is still top secret so I can’t show you it now, but don’t worry – I’ve scheduled a shoot.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAcross the forecourt, a more nondescript shed houses even spicier machines.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"chapter-the-best-wrc-garage-that-isn-t\"\u003eThe Best WRC Garage That Isn’t\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/06214438/TobyThyerPhotography-21.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/06214438/TobyThyerPhotography-21-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"TobyThyerPhotography-21\" data-attachment-id=\"652802\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/06214438/TobyThyerPhotography-21.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/workshop-keeping-subaru-wrc-cars-japanese-public-roads/tobythyerphotography-21-22/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/06214438/TobyThyerPhotography-21-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/06214506/TobyThyerPhotography-27-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"TobyThyerPhotography-27\" data-attachment-id=\"652808\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazo